main event: A UFO report from 10th December 1953 in the Maryland area concluded the sighting of a meteor moving horizontally.
interesting points: The report contains no photographs or physical evidence.
Observers described the object as having a gray color and being approximately 45 feet long.
Witnesses of the event included military and civilian personnel.
The report includes details of the object's altitude and flight path.
A separate newspaper report mentioned a strange greenish-blue light in the sky, spotted by RCAF observers, with no satisfactory explanation given.
